Class LinkParameterHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jactr.core.utils.parameter.ParameterHandler<IAssociativeLink>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IParameterHandler<IAssociativeLink>

    public class LinkParameterHandler
extends ParameterHandler<IAssociativeLink>
    basic parameter handler that returns Link4 based on one of two string patterns: "(iChunkName count strength)" or "(iChunkName count strength FNiCj)"
